name: NHIF Items and ERPNext items
query:
SELECT icd.ref_code as "NHIF Item Code", icd.parent AS "Item:Link/Item:200", MAX(n.itemname) as "NHIF Item Name"
    FROM `tabItem Customer Detail` icd
    INNER JOIN `tabItem` i ON i.name = icd.parent
    LEFT OUTER JOIN `tabNHIF Price Package` n ON icd.ref_code = n.itemcode
    WHERE icd.customer_name = 'NHIF'
    GROUP BY icd.ref_code , icd.parent
